Database Tables: 

Department
    - id int
    - name varchar(30)

Role 
    - id int
    - title varchar(30)
    - salary decimal 
    - department_id int 

Employee
    - id int
    - first_name varchar(30)
    - last_name varchar(30)
    - role_id int
    - manager_id int (references employee table)

Inquirer Options: 
    - View All Departments
    - View All Roles
    - View All Employees
    - Add a Department
    - Add an Employee
    - Update an Employee Role

